## Professional Summary

Network Engineer with 10+ years in IT infrastructure and security, including hands-on experience managing 98 customer sites and 492 network devices across 14 states. Background includes Zero Trust implementation at enterprise scale (Elevance Health, 500+ systems) and network security supporting 600+ hospital locations (TruBridge). Track record of identifying operational inefficiencies and building automated solutions that deliver measurable business value.

